Develop tools to assist research managers in developing hypotheses, interpreting results and optimizing network adaptation strategies. The purpose of this innovation partnership is to develop tools to help researchers develop hypotheses, interpret results and optimize network adaptation strategies.
The Innovation Partnership will be broken down into the following three phases:
• Phase 1: design of an innovative prototype;
• Phase 2: development of the solution and testing in operational conditions;
• Phase 3: Acquisition of the solution for commercialization.
